    "steam_appid": 3122270,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122270/extras/3189308705bb2e7843553373b4494b30.avif?t=1728562321\" width=616 height=318 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A?</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your main goal is to escape from the so-called, surreal and confusing, &quot;<strong>Klobgniak's Home</strong>&quot; and if possible, solve Klobgniak's mystery and find his hideout. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122270/extras/1cd31e3efcdd8dd11806e962c1caec2e.avif?t=1728562321\" width=616 height=318 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MAKING NOISE</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try not to make noise and be well hidden. <strong>Walking</strong>, <strong>running</strong>, <strong>jumping</strong> and other <strong>interactions with the environment</strong> can be heard, so wait for the right moment to act.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In several rooms there are small &quot;<strong>homes</strong>&quot; where you can hide. While you're hidden here you cannot be spotted or &quot;<strong>Returned</strong>&quot;. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122270/extras/5563bc5d243096038cd8236d2a9b911b.avif?t=1728562321\" width=616 height=330 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RETURNED</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you're <strong>Returned</strong>, you'll have to start over and all the progress you've made will be lost. When that happens, some <strong>items</strong> that will be important for you to make progress could be <strong>hidden in different, random locations and places</strong>, and sometimes, some kind of <strong>tool</strong> will be needed to get to them. If you are caught with some <strong>Klobgniak's items</strong>, you will be <strong>punished</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122270/extras/24c70a7befd6a07d5daecfb3fc309f9a.avif?t=1728562321\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PUNISHMENT</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;Rebels and thieves must be punished.&quot;</strong> While you are punished, your movement is restricted. You are required to <strong>pay</strong> to remove the punishment. However, you could escape without paying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Good luck! </strong></p>",
